# Graffiti: Blood Tax

**Location / Context:** Often found sprayed over corporate logos of Earth or Mars-based companies on Ceres.
**Visual Description:** Angry, thick strokes. Sometimes includes a stylized list of Belter casualties or grievances.

**English Text:**
> __inner#CL2 pay#CL2 INSTR credit#CL10 belter#CL2 pay#CL2 INSTR blood.#CL6 remember#IMP station#CL9 Anderson.__
"Inners pay with credits, Belters pay with blood. Remember Anderson Station."
